WEBVTT

00:01:28.032 --> 00:01:30.413
Kada taj govornik 
onda ode korak dalje

00:01:30.413 --> 00:01:32.089
i misli suprotno 
od onoga što govori

00:01:32.089 --> 00:01:35.294
i pokušava da bude 
pomalo zajedljiv i zao,

00:01:35.294 --> 00:01:37.137
kao da ismeva nešto,

00:01:37.137 --> 00:01:38.797
onda imate sarkazam.

00:01:38.797 --> 00:01:40.465
Uzmimo drugi primer:

00:01:40.465 --> 00:01:41.548
"Super si to uradio!"

00:01:41.548 --> 00:01:43.954
Neko je ostvario 
svoj životni san:

00:01:43.954 --> 00:01:44.748
super!

00:01:44.748 --> 00:01:46.810
Neko je pobedio
na sportskom takmičenju:

00:01:46.810 --> 00:01:47.667
super!

00:01:47.667 --> 00:01:50.047
Neko otpozadi udari 
drugi automobil:

00:01:50.047 --> 00:01:52.724
nije super.

00:01:52.724 --> 00:01:56.441
Kada saputnik kaže:
"Super si to uradio!",

00:01:56.441 --> 00:01:57.969
on verovatno misli 
suprotno od toga

00:01:57.969 --> 00:02:00.191
sa naznakama ismevanja.